--------------------------------------------------------------------
Licensing Notice
--------------------------------------------------------------------

Because this repository contains different types of work, each part is licensed separately:

- electronics/ – Electronics designs (schematics, PCB files, simulations)
  Licensed under CERN Open Hardware Licence Strongly Reciprocal (CERN-OHL-S v2).
  Full text: https://ohwr.org/cern_ohl_s_v2.pdf

- mechanics/ – Mechanical designs (3D models, CAD, STL, drawings)
  Licensed under CERN Open Hardware Licence Strongly Reciprocal (CERN-OHL-S v2).
  Full text: https://ohwr.org/cern_ohl_s_v2.pdf

- software/ – Firmware and applications
  Licensed under Mozilla Public License v2.0 (MPL-2.0).
  Full text: https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/MPL/2.0/

--------------------------------------------------------------------
Contributor Notice
--------------------------------------------------------------------

By contributing to this repository, you agree that your contributions will be licensed under the same terms as the folder they belong to:

- Contributions to electronics/ → licensed under CERN-OHL-S v2
- Contributions to mechanics/  → licensed under CERN-OHL-S v2
- Contributions to software/   → licensed under MPL v2.0

--------------------------------------------------------------------
Summary of Obligations
--------------------------------------------------------------------

- You may freely use, modify, manufacture, and distribute this project.
- If you distribute hardware (electronics or mechanics) based on this project,
  you must provide the complete corresponding source under CERN-OHL-S v2.
- If you modify files covered by MPL v2.0 (firmware/software),
  you must publish those modified files under MPL v2.0.
- You may combine MPL-covered software with closed-source code,
  provided that the MPL-covered files remain open.

